Good deal for two great Julia Roberts films.  I mostly bought this for Stepmom (I tear up every time, and I'm usually like that), but I also enjoy Mona Lisa Smile, so bonus :)

I could have done without the pink spine and framing around the movie pics on the front.  It's a small thing,  but I arrange my movies by genre, then by color (I'm neurotic like that), and it looks weird hanging out btw Clueless, Down With Love, Legally Blonde, and Mean Girls :p
